---
title: Teriyaki Ginger Beef Rump & Creamy Slaw Bowl with Garlic Rice & Parsley
description: Our favourite thing about a slaw bowl is how easy it is to add variety to it! This one combines garlic rice with creamy pear slaw, topped off with tender strips of beef in a fragrant ginger and teriyaki glaze. Let’s add a final flourish with crispy shallots, and you’re ready to jump in!
